{{vgname|侧影幻像|ja=シルエットミラージュ ～リプログラムド ホープ～|en=Silhouette Mirage}}是一款由[[Treasure|Treasure]]公司制作的横向卷轴类游戏。游戏最初于1997年9月10日在[[世嘉土星|世嘉土星]]上发行。<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamefaqs.com/saturn/574615-silhouette-mirage/data| title = Release information| publisher = [[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]| date = | accessdate = 2016-04-11| language = en| archive-date = 2016-12-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161220003639/http://www.gamefaqs.com/saturn/574615-silhouette-mirage/data| dead-url = no}}</ref> 游戏后移植至[[PlayStation_(游戏机)|PlayStation]]。

游戏设定在地球末日后的2000年。游戏是动作类横向卷轴类游戏，与《[[銀河快槍手|銀河快槍手]]》玩法类似。

游戏收到不同高低的分数。《[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]》的Peter Bartholow给予PlayStation版本4.6/10的分数<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/silhouette-mirage-review/1900-2549299/|title=Silhouette Mirage Review - GameSpot|last=Bartholow|first=Peter|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|date=January 21, 2000|accessdate=October 7, 2015|archive-date=2019-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190623155000/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/silhouette-mirage-review/1900-2549299/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而Dave's Sega Saturn Page的Michael Motoda给予最初世嘉版本9.5/10的分数。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sega-saturn.com/saturn/software/reviews/silhouette-3.htm/|title=Dave's Sega Saturn & PC Games Page - Reader Review|last=Motoda|first=Michael|date=1997|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810203037/http://sega-saturn.com/saturn/software/reviews/silhouette-3.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

